<section class="oe_container">
    <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
        <h2 class="oe_slogan">Labour Cost Booking</h2>
        <div class="oe_span6">
            <div class="oe_row_img oe_centered">
                <img class="oe_picture" src="odoo_labour_cost.png">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="oe_span6">
            <p class="oe_mt32">

            <li>	Create Employees 	</li>
            <li>Link User and Home address in Employee Master	</li>
            <li>Employee Time Sheet Product 	</li>
            <li>Product Master > Product Type = Service 	</li>
            <li>Set the product cost (overhead rate) and selling price (for estimation)	</li>
            <li>Set Job Labour Cost Account as revenue and expense account 	</li>
            <li>Labour Cost to WIP [ Contracting > Job Costing > Labaour Cost ]	</li>
            <li>Total hours spent for the project from hr timesheet activities	</li>
            <li>Calculating overhead rate from the service product cost linked in employee master multiplied by the hours worked in each project.	</li>
            <li>Actual Amount is calculated from gross salary of the employee divided by total working hours for the month  multiplied by the hours worked in each project.	</li>
            <li>In Validation WIP Account will be Debited and Provision account (Job Labour Cost Account) will be credited	</li>
            <li>If Actual rate is ticked Actual amount is posted otherwise overhead amount is posted in journal entries	</li>




            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<section class="oe_container oe_dark">
    <div class="oe_row oe_spaced">
        <h2 class="oe_slogan">Material Issue</h2>
        <div class="oe_span6">
            <p class="oe_mt32">
<li>	Create Type Of Operation in Warehouse Material Issue</li>
<li>	Source - WH/Stock	</li>
<li>	Destination - Partners Location/Customers	</li>
<li>	Create Stock Move - All operation > Material Issue	</li>
<li>	Select the Project /Analytic in stock Picking	</li>
<li>	Journal Entries - Account Move	</li>
<li>	Inventory will be Credited with Analytic Account	</li>
<li>	WIP Account will be Debited with Analytic Account	</li>

            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="oe_span6">
            <div class="oe_row_img oe_centered">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

